<div> </div>
<h2><a name="Itinerary"></a>Itinerary</h2>
<p><strong>Day 1 (Monday or Friday) </strong>Fly to Stavanger, where a transfer will be waiting to take you to your harbour front hotel (approx. 20 minutes). </p>
<p><strong>Day 2 (Tuesday or Saturday) </strong>A visit to the Preisketolen ‘Pulpit Rock’ is a must, and guests can choose whether to take the Lysefjord cruise, the cruise &amp; hike option to ascend the rock, or an ‘Off the Beaten Track’ guided hike. The ‘Swords in Rock’ monument is another important stop for many visitors, as are the amazing ‘Flor &amp; Fjære’ gardens, located on a remote island approximately 20 minutes outside of Stavanger centre. A selection of museums also provide an interesting insight into the history and culture of the area.</p>
<p><strong>Day 4 or 5 (Friday or Monday) </strong>A memorable cruise along the fjord coast north to <a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen">Bergen</a> on the new Fjordline ferry route. With comfortable seating and buffet breakfast included on board, you can just sit back and enjoy the scenery – it’s a great alternative to the usual transfers by road as it takes you past the many fjord coast islands. </p>
<p><strong>Day 5 or 6 (Saturday or Tuesday) </strong>First morning waking up in Bergen, you have plenty of time to explore this wonderful city. After visiting the main attractions of the fish market, Bryggen Wharf and museums, why not head up the Fløiban funicular for walking trails, panoramic city views and canoeing at the ‘Shoemaker’s Lake’. Visit Edvard Greig’s house for an introduction to his life and piano recital of some of his works, try one of the city’s new food tours, or even discover the old.</p>
<p><strong>Day 8 (Monday or Friday) </strong>Return to Bergen airport for your flight back to the UK, or transfer by boat to Balestrand for guests extending their holiday.</p>
<p><strong>Extend your stay </strong>Guests may choose to add a stay in the quiet village of <a data-udi="umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377}" title="Balestrand">Balestrand</a> on the Sognefjord at the end of their holiday. Transfers to/from Bergen are by 4-hour coastal express boat are included.</p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>What’s included</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK into Stavanger and back from Bergen (some supplements may apply)</li>
<li>Return transfers to and from the airport</li>
<li>Scenic transfer by 5-hour coastal cruise on Fjordline ferry line from Stavanger to Bergen</li>
<li>Accommodation with private facilities throughout</li>
<li>Bed &amp; Breakfast in Stavanger &amp; Bergen</li>
<li>'Meet &amp; Greet' service throughout your stay, with a welcome to the resort and 24/7 phone service</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Departure dates</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Depart on any date throughout the summer, as long as it's a Monday or Friday</li>
<li>Monday departures = 4 nights Stavanger, 3 nights Bergen (+4 nights in Balestrand if extending to 11 nights at end of stay)</li>
<li>Friday departures = 3 nights Stavanger, 4 nights Bergen (+ 3 nights in Balestrand if extending to 10 nights at end of stay)</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Your Hotels</strong></p>
<p><strong>Accommodation: </strong>Guests will have a choice of either 'standard' hotels or 'superior' hotels.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Hotels</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Stavanger</strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/39c8ec436eee4726adc26984ed656337" href="/{localLink:umb://document/39c8ec436eee4726adc26984ed656337}" title="Hotel Victoria">Hotel Victoria</a> ★★★</li>
<li><strong>Bergen</strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/0d46aba9adc646f2afb1eeefe50bbc3f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0d46aba9adc646f2afb1eeefe50bbc3f}" title="Augustin Hotel">Hotel Augustin</a> ★★★+</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Superior Hotels </strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Stavanger</strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/b8b5a6ba0dbd4b7bbbd353ea7f8b9339" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8b5a6ba0dbd4b7bbbd353ea7f8b9339}" title="Clarion Skagen Brygge">Clarion Collection Skagen Brygge</a> ★★★★</li>
<li><strong>Bergen</strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/9d0bff3ead764e2784c07e601d199b65" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9d0bff3ead764e2784c07e601d199b65}" title="First Hotel Marin">Hotel First Marin</a> ★★★★</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Departure flights to Ålesund from:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Gatwick</li>
<li>Or indirect flights via Amsterdam from regional airports available on request</li>
<li>Flight supplements may apply</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
