  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;"><strong>Standard Hotels</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;">Stavanger <a data-udi="umb://document/39c8ec436eee4726adc26984ed656337" href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/39c8ec436eee4726adc26984ed656337%7d" title="Hotel Victoria">Hotel Victoria</a> ★★★ <span>Dating back to 1900, this traditional friendly hotel, located right on the harbour front next to the boat quay, provides an excellent base from which to explore this fascinating city and beyond. The town centre for the many museums, shops, restaurants and the boat harbour for excursions are just on your doorstep.</span><br />Bergen <a data-udi="umb://document/0d46aba9adc646f2afb1eeefe50bbc3f" href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/0d46aba9adc646f2afb1eeefe50bbc3f%7d" title="Augustin Hotel">Hotel Augustin</a> ★★★ <span>A friendly family-run hotel, beautifully decorated with a welcoming atmosphere and many special touches. Centrally situated which makes the harbour, fish market and Bryggen Wharf approximately a 3-4 minute walk (350m). This hotel is a great choice to explore this fascinating city, conveniently located to shops and a good selection of international restaurants.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;"><strong>OR</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;"><strong>Superior Hotels</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;">Stavanger <a data-udi="umb://document/b8b5a6ba0dbd4b7bbbd353ea7f8b9339" href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/b8b5a6ba0dbd4b7bbbd353ea7f8b9339%7d" title="Clarion Skagen Brygge">Hotel Clarion Skagen Brygge</a> ★★★★ <span>This stylish hotel has been newly-renovated throughout to a high standard in a modern-style and is one of the most recognisable buildings in Stavanger and enjoys lovely views across the harbour and old town opposite. All the bedrooms have been recently-renovated and a complimentary light buffet evening meal is included for all guests.</span><br />Bergen <a data-udi="umb://document/9d0bff3ead764e2784c07e601d199b65" href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/9d0bff3ead764e2784c07e601d199b65%7d" title="First Hotel Marin">Hotel First Marin</a> ★★★+ <span>In an enviable, harbour front location, convenient for Bergen’s main attractions, this elegant hotel offers good facilities and spacious, comfortable rooms.  Located in an old wharf building, Bergen's main sights of the harbour, fish market and Fløiban funicular are only a few steps away.</span></p>]]></roomsDescription>
